<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0;">To</span><span style="--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF;"> run the latest Copter binary (downloading binaries if needed):</span></span>
