<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;">Once you have available ports you can connect your DroneKit script to one </span><span style="--shiki-light:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF;">UDP</span><span style="--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;"> address </span><span style="--shiki-light:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583;">and</span><span style="--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;"> your Ground Control Station to another.</span></span>
